title: Yevgeni Tsimbal
text:
Yevgeni Dmitriyevich Tsimbal (; born 11 February 1986) is a Russian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Kuban-Holding%20Pavlovskaya">FC Kuban-Holding Pavlovskaya</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Baltika%20Kaliningrad">FC Baltika Kaliningrad</a> on 19 April 2008 in a game against <a href="FC%20Metallurg-Kuzbass%20Novokuznetsk">FC Metallurg-Kuzbass Novokuznetsk</a>.
